      <title>特鲁多承诺再提供数十亿美元的公寓建设贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trudeau-pledges-billions-more-for-apartment-construction-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多表示，即将出台的联邦预算将在公寓建设贷款计划中再投入 150 亿加元（合 111 亿美元），这是他为解决加拿大人口激增导致的住房短缺问题所做的最新努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trudeau-pledges-billions-more-for-apartment-construction-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 14:21:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科尔尼调查显示中东成为外国直接投资的重点地区</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/middle-east-emerges-as-key-region-for-fdi-in-kearney-survey</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项对未来三年最有可能吸引资金的国家进行排名的调查显示，中东日益成为寻求部署资本的外国投资者最理想的地点之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/middle-east-emerges-as-key-region-for-fdi-in-kearney-survey</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>寻求庇护者的涌入令加拿大感到惊讶，城市承担了成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/influx-of-asylum-seekers-surprises-canada-and-cities-bear-the-cost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[寻求庇护的新移民数量创历史新高，加拿大城市不堪重负，预算紧张，临时庇护所超出了其承受能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/influx-of-asylum-seekers-surprises-canada-and-cities-bear-the-cost</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 13:24:08 GMT</pubDate>
